Zvauri kutsvaga, mumwe munhu anezvo.

0:21:19.940,0:21:22.760
Mwari akatuma mumwe munhu kuti abatsire kunhadziridza ramangwana rako

0:21:22.760,0:21:29.860
uye kuti mumwe munhu akamirira kuti ubatsire mumwe munhu anenge achida rubatsiro rwako.

0:21:29.860,0:21:40.440
