0:21:40.440,0:21:42.400
Ndatenda.

0:21:42.400,0:21:43.460
Komborerwa!

0:21:43.460,0:21:44.920
(Ameni!)

0:21:44.920,0:21:55.680
Saka ikozvino, chinhu chine nyasha kwauri kuti uzive kuti mumwe munhu akamirira iwe, anoda rubatsiro rwako.

0:21:55.680,0:21:59.500
Mumwe munhu ari kumirira rubatsiro rwako.

0:21:59.500,0:22:02.640
Mumwe munhu ari kumirira munyengetero wako.

0:22:02.640,0:22:07.980
Mumwe munhu ari kumirira chii? Rubatsiro

0:22:07.980,0:22:15.680
Ungataura neni here taura neni? Taura neni!

