0:22:33.180,0:22:35.760
Ichi chinhu chakavakwa.

0:22:35.760,0:22:40.440
Iwe ndiwe Chechi; vaka vanhu

0:22:40.440,0:22:45.640
Enda unovaka vanhu; usavaka makereke.

0:22:45.640,0:22:48.420
Ichi chinhu chakagadzirwa, chivakwa.

0:22:48.420,0:22:52.480
Iwe ndiwe Chechi chaiyo iri kutaurwa ne Bhaibheri

0:22:52.480,0:23:00.360
Chechi ichakuvaka; iwe unogona kuvaka kereke.

0:23:00.360,0:23:09.220
Tinofanira kutaura zvakawanda nezvekuvaka vanhu - simba re vanhu.

0:23:09.220,0:23:10.720
Nderipi shoko rauri kutora kuenda naro kumba?

0:23:10.720,0:23:14.340
Pane munhu angasimuka kundiudza shoko rauri kutora kumba?

0:23:14.340,0:23:16.360
Mukoma ... ndatenda.

0:23:16.360,0:23:19.280
Munhu wose ane chimwe chinhu chokupa.

0:23:19.280,0:23:21.620
Mazvita.

0:23:21.620,0:23:26.100
Kana iwe usingazivi kuti iwe unoda zvakadini Mwari mune chinhu chiduku, iwe hauzozivi kuti

0:23:26.100,0:23:28.060
unoda Mwari mune chinhu chikuru.

0:23:28.060,0:23:31.540
Mwari ane hanya kwazvo nezvinhu zvishoma.

0:23:31.540,0:23:35.360
Kuti zvakawanda zviuye, paradzana nazvo. Batsira vanoshayiwa

0:23:35.360,0:23:40.060
Ndatenda - murovererei maoko.

0:23:40.060,0:23:42.060
Pane mumwewo?

0:23:42.060,0:23:44.480
Zvidzidzo zviviri zvandiri kutora

0:23:44.480,0:23:52.000
Chokutanga: "Mwari ane hanya kwazvo nezvinhu zvishoma".

0:23:52.000,0:23:53.960
Chechipiri: ...

0:23:53.960,0:23:58.820
Ndechekuti Mwari ane hanya zvikuru nezvinhu zviduku.

0:23:58.820,0:24:01.320
Uye "zvinhu zviduku" izvi idimikira.

0:24:01.320,0:24:02.560
- Ehe. - Zvakanaka.

0:24:02.560,0:24:05.020
Chii chaunonzwisisa pamusoro pe "zvinhu zviduku", changamire?

0:24:05.020,0:24:07.060
Zvinogona kuva zvinhu zvako.

0:24:07.060,0:24:09.680
- Ndatenda; pfuma shoma. - Zvinhu zvishoma.

0:24:09.680,0:24:11.120
- Ndatenda. - Mari shoma yaunayo.

0:24:11.120,0:24:15.140
Ndatenda; muombererei.

0:24:15.140,0:24:18.340
Iwe wateerera kune izvozvo? Zvishoma

0:24:18.340,0:24:22.180
Mwari ane hanya kwazvo nezvinhu zviduku.

0:24:22.180,0:24:23.380
Zviduku izvozvo zvinoreva...

0:24:23.380,0:24:30.460
Ari kutaura pamusoro pevari pakati ne pakati, vane zvishoma.

0:24:30.460,0:24:33.760
Zvatinoona se zvishoma?

0:24:33.760,0:24:37.660
Sei Ane han'a nazvo?

0:24:37.660,0:24:42.140
Nokuti tinofanira kuzvibata zvakanaka kwazvo.

0:24:42.140,0:24:53.520
Kuti zvidiki izvozvo zvikure, tinofanira kunge takagadzirira kupa izvozvo sechirikadzi murombo

0:24:53.520,0:24:58.340
nokuti zvakawanda zvinogona kusauya.

0:24:58.340,0:25:03.080
Svondo Ye Musi We Svondo Mu SCOAN

0:25:03.080,0:25:17.880
Uye zvirinyore, zviri nyore chaizvo kupa nezvishoma.

0:25:17.880,0:25:29.900
Iwe unogona kupa zvakanakisa ne zvishoma zvaunazvo, asi zvakaoma kwazvo kupa zvakanakisa kana une zvakawanda.

0:25:29.900,0:25:38.360
Iwe unorangarira murume mupfumi, uyo zvaive zvakaoma kutengesa zvinhu zvake.

0:25:38.360,0:25:46.080
Akati iye akanga asingazivi kuti aitangira papi.

0:25:46.080,0:25:49.460
Nokuti unogona chete kupa izvo zvausingadi.

0:25:49.460,0:25:55.880
Kana vanhu vapfumi vachida kupa, vanogaropa zvavasingadi.

0:25:55.880,0:26:02.740
Kana iwe ukasangana namamiriyoneya, akapfuma - kana iwe wakasangana navo ...

0:26:02.740,0:26:10.200
Dai Jesu akasangana navo, zvavaizoita - vaizozarura magaraji avo.

0:26:10.200,0:26:14.220
Zvavanenge vachizopa hazvisi izvo zvinhu zvavanoshandisa zvino

0:26:14.220,0:26:17.720
Izvi ndizvo zvinhu zvakarongedzwa kwemakore mazhinji.

0:26:17.720,0:26:23.720
Zvichiri zvakanaka, asi havachazvida zvakare.

0:26:23.720,0:26:35.000
Vapfumi vanowanzopa zvavasingadi, asi varombo vanopa izvo upenyu hwavo hunotemba nazvo.

0:26:35.000,0:26:43.680
Svondo Ye Musi We Svondo Mu SCOAN

0:26:43.680,0:26:46.040
Iwe unoda kutaura chimwe chinhu? Huya tione!

0:26:46.040,0:26:54.980
Shoko rimwe chete randinotora kubva pano; Ndinofanira kugara ndichiziva kuti pane umwe munhu anoda ini.

0:26:54.980,0:26:57.140
anoda ne zvangu.

