Hazvina mhosva kuti une zvishoma zvakadini, mumwe munhu ari kuda iwe.

0:27:05.480,0:27:11.580
Udza waugere naye, "Hazvina mhosva kuti une zvishoma zvakadini, mumwe munhu ari kukuda iwe."

0:27:11.580,0:27:20.120
Hazvina mhosva kuti une zvishoma zvakadini, zvisinei kuti une mari shoma sei,

0:27:20.120,0:27:32.620
zvisinei kuti iwe une zvinhu zvishoma zvakadini, mumwe munhu ari kukuda iwe.

0:27:32.620,0:27:39.780
Ndadzidzawo kuti tinowanzopa nguva yakanaka kuna Mwari apo isu tiri munhuwo zvake.

0:27:39.780,0:27:40.280
Mazvita.

0:27:40.280,0:27:43.480
Asi patinenge tave munhu wepamusoro hatina nguva yakanaka ya Mwari.

0:27:43.480,0:27:45.500
Iwe wateerera kune izvozvo?

0:27:45.500,0:27:47.860
Apo tinenge tiri munhuwo zvake ...

0:27:47.860,0:28:00.740
Kana tichiti munhuwo zvake zvimwe unozviona uri wemhuri yako, kubasa kwako kana kereke yako.

0:28:00.740,0:28:07.720
Kana chimwe chinhu chikaitika kwauri, paunenge uri muduku, kereke yako inotarisira, mhuri yako inochema,

0:28:07.720,0:28:09.620
vanhu vekubasa kwako vanotambudzika.

0:28:09.620,0:28:11.880
Ava ndivo vanhu vanokuziva iwe.

0:28:11.880,0:28:24.340
Asi paunenge wakuzivikanwa zvakanyanya kwose kwose, uye iwe unova mukuru une mukurumbira

0:28:24.340,0:28:39.300
zvinogara zvakaoma kupa kubva pahuwandu ne hupfumi - zvakanyanya kuoma.

0:28:39.300,0:28:43.320
Kunze kwekuti iwe wakanga uchipa apo waive muduku ...

0:28:43.320,0:28:48.800
Kana waipa apo waive uri muduku, paunova mukuru,

0:28:48.800,0:28:52.040
iwe ucharamba uchipa zvinoenderana nemirairo ya Mwari

0:28:52.040,0:29:00.760
asi kana iwe uchiti, 'Kusvikira ndava mukuru ndipo pandichatanga kupa', zvizhinji hazvizombouya.

0:29:00.760,0:29:11.320
Kana Mwari achida kukusimudzira, Achakusimudzira kune zvido zvevamwe.

0:29:11.320,0:29:16.400
Svondo Ye Musi We Svondo Mu SCOAN

0:29:16.400,0:29:23.080
Unoziva; kune maporomosheni maviri - poromosheni ya Mwari uye poromosheni yadhiyabhorosi.

0:29:23.080,0:29:29.360
"Sekupa kwandakaita mari yacho, kwete sekupa kunoita nyika."

0:29:29.360,0:29:37.640
Nyika inogona kukupa mari, pfuma, kukusimudzira asi kwete sekupa kunoita Mwari.

0:29:37.640,0:29:41.460
Mwari anopa norugare nemufaro.

0:29:41.460,0:29:51.980
Pane mirairo yakabatana nasatani, poromosheni yadhiyabhorosi, iyo munhu achabhadhara zvikuru.

0:29:51.980,0:29:54.460
Iwe wakaponeswa kuponesa vamwe.

0:29:54.460,0:29:56.900
Iwe wakaropafadzwa kuropafadza vamwe.

0:29:56.900,0:30:02.480
Kana iwe usati wagadzirira kukomborera vamwe, hapana chikonzero chokukukomborera.

0:30:02.480,0:30:05.660
Chikonzero chekukuropafadza ndeche kuti uropafadze vamwe.

0:30:05.660,0:30:09.040
Kana zvisiri muhurongwa hwako zvako kuropafadza vamwe -

0:30:09.040,0:30:13.540
Mwari anoziva mwoyo yenyu uye Anoziva zvichazoitika mberi.

0:30:13.540,0:30:16.840
Iwe uri muridzi wa zvino uye Mwari ndiye muridzi we mangwana.

0:30:16.840,0:30:25.300
Kana Mwari achiziva kuti hauzovepo kune varombo nevanoshayiwa, zvakawanda hazvizombouya.

0:30:25.300,0:30:36.060
