0:30:36.060,0:30:40.460
zvizhinji hazvizombouya ".

0:30:40.460,0:30:43.260
Ndinokutendai, changamire. Garai pasi.

0:30:43.260,0:30:47.920
Tora peni yako uzvinyore pasi - Ndinofunga kuti izvi zvakanaka kwauri.

0:30:47.920,0:31:07.020
Kana Mwari achiziva kuti hauzovepo kune varombo, nherera, shirikadzi ne pfunda - zvakawanda hazvizombouya.

0:31:07.020,0:31:12.300
Ndicho chikonzero vazhinji vedu vari kunetseka neurombo ne matambudziko.

0:31:12.300,0:31:18.960
Tinoramba tichinyengetera kuti tive vapfumi kwemakore akawanda, asi zvakadaro - hapana chikomborero,

0:31:18.960,0:31:21.940
nokuti iwe haugovere zvishoma zvaunazvo

